title: Top 10 Linebacker Rankings: Who takes top spot after Luke Kuechly's retirement? (Football 7/9)
description:
Defensive positional rankings wrap up on the Pick Six podcast as we take a look at the Top 10 linebackers in the league with first-time guest Jordan Dajani. Jordan joins Will Brinson to discuss the youngsters on the list that could easily climb after this season, the veterans that are finally making their mark and the mainstay at the top of the list that could be on his way to the Hall of Fame.
